{
  "stem": "11671.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was put in camp under the British guard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Palestine, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to Athlit, which was a gathering point for all the incoming illegal immigrants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Athlit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then another camp-- I think it was called Qiryat Shemu'el, something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was specially set up-- after they processed your papers and made sure that you were an immigrant with the immigration papers, and you weren't sick, and you didn't bring in any diseases.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were put in this camp for a whole month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first time Harold came to visit me in this camp under the British guard, and I-- was barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't come in just from the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I stuck my hand out through the barbed wire to shake his hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't even know I was scratched or that I was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's how we-- the first time we met.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the British Guard said 10 minutes were up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the way we established contact was, when I got into Palestine, I wrote a little note on a piece of paper and threw it out the window to a little girl, about 12 year old.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I wrote on it to please bring it to the Technion, where Harold was studying under the GI Bill, because the British wouldn't let people in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he went on the pretense of being a student.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he was studying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this little piece of paper said in Hebrew, [HEBREW]. 'I have arrived.' And this little girl made sure that Harold got it at the Technion.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's how he found out that I have arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just met there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Reunited.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to wait until I was liberated completely out of camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
